# NOTE: Cargo.lock is intentionally NOT ignored. This is a deployable binary
# crate, and the pinned ed25519-dalek 2.1.1 (which fixes a rand_core version
# diamond in soroban-env-host's testutils) lives only in the lockfile. Ignoring
# it would let a fresh checkout re-resolve to the broken ed25519-dalek 3.0.0.

